      <title>Hexo部署到阿里云云</title>
      <link href="2020/10/13/hello-world/"/>
      <url>2020/10/13/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##一.云服务器配置Git</p><p>1.安装依赖库</p><pre><code>yum install curl-devel expat-devel gettext-devel openssl-devel zlib-devel</code></pre><p>2.安装编译工具</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">yum <span class="token function">install</span> gcc perl-ExtUtils-MakeMaker package</code></pre><p>3.查看git的版本y</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">git</span> version</code></pre><p>4.删除git</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">yum remove <span class="token function">git</span> -y</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
